                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/75f79ad4-3eb9-11e3-a21b-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/75f79ad4-3eb9-11e3-a21b-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_75 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;add mds1 failed for new params&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

